data.description: This Alora floorplan home embraces the qualities of inviting, spacious, open concept living as well as the low maintenance courtyard & backyard.    The ideal resort lifestyle is right here &   landscaped to maximize fun & minimize upkeep.  From it's fully pavered courtyard, to it's backyard with heated pool & spa, travertine decking, firepit, built-in BBQ, and synthetic turf, it's ready for you to entertain or relax inside and out!  Custom bar area with keg & bev fridge and quartz countertop combine function with luxury.  The white kitchen is calling your name with it's expansive island, wall oven, gas cooktop, beverage fridge and large pantry/smartspace.  And to top it off, there are 3 bedrooms all with ensuites.  Did I mention 3-car garage?? Arizona Living is Right here waiting for you!
